name: campusnet-electron
description: Get all your DTU course files synced to your computer

packageJSON.name: campusnet-electron
packageJSON.description: Sync CampusNet files to your computer

scripts.pack: source .config && npm run compile && build --arch all --platform darwin win32
scripts.dist: source .config && npm run compile && build --arch all --platform darwin win32
scripts.release:osx: source .config && npm run compile && build --dist --platform darwin --publish always
scripts.release:win: source .config && npm run compile && build --dist --platform win32 --arch ia32 --publish always
scripts.release: npm run release:osx && npm run release:win
scripts.publish-gh-pages: git subtree push --prefix gh-pages/build origin gh-pages

releases.name: v1.0.7
releases.body: - Makes auto update work for windows
